#

Spicy Chickpea and Quinoa Bowl

30 min
$8
450 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 2

Dietary Tags:

vegetariangluten-freehigh-protein

Cuisine:

AmericanMediterranean

Course:

mainlunchdinner

Tags:

healthyquick mealone bowlspicy

Description

A hearty and healthy bowl combining spicy chickpeas and fluffy quinoa, vibrant with fresh vegetables.

Ingredients

  • cooked quinoa: 1 cup
  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz), rinsed and drained
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • cumin: 1 teaspoon
  • paprika: 1 teaspoon
  • cayenne pepper: 1/2 teaspoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • fresh spinach: 2 cups
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup, halved
  • avocado: 1, sliced
  • lime juice: 1 tablespoon
